_sText:
This is the smaller, more detailed and better version of awp_snowdream. With the same theme, but a different layout.

Maptype: Awp
Number of Player: 32 (recommended 24)

This is also compatible with deathmatch.

The boxes and shapes are customly made into icecubes just for the beauty of it.
There is also falling snow and a start up sound, to give players the feel of being in the mountainous region.

Credits to BenTheKuno for his amazing icemt skybox texture

Please inform me of bugs found that need to be fixed or anything that you wish to be improved.

Please assess my map also. :)

Thanks and have fun!
